bokAa। kampiuTAa sAYena niYe pa.DaAshonA karaCilia, Thia ACea। nAhaa nijea praYojane hyAa paryana karate pArisaa, tAo mene nilAmaa। kintu tAi bale eramaa! bhAbaCea haliuDea kono ekaTA sAi-aphAi gala phe.NdeCia? nAa, sAi-aphAi naYaa, tabe galpea plaa sAi-ahAbaa। chenA chenA lAgaCea? oi ye yakhaa kono gabeshaNAa pepAa khu.Njate giYe prakAshaa s.nsthAguloa phea ka.Dai mAkho tea goCea a' TAkA dAo sAbaskrAia karoa' lekhA dekhe piCiYe Asenaa, takhaa sudUa kAjAkistAnea ekaratti jedi ekaTA meYea tairi ekaTA oYebasAia ApanAke binAmUlye dAmi dAmi saa gabeshaNApata hAtea muThoa ene deYaa। oi halo AmAdea bokA meYea, AlekajAndrA AshAnobhanA elabAkiYAnaa।
pa.DaAshonA shuru kareCia nijea jAYagAteia, kAjAkistAnea। pa.Daate pa.Daate dekhalo sekhAnea inTAraneTe saa kiCua opari bejAa nishedhAjnAa। paCandea gAa shonA yAbenAa, sinemA dekhA yAbenAa, mAa paCandea bi pa.DaAa jana o hAjAro niYamaa, beshirabhAa bio TAkA diYe kine DAunaloa karate hachCea। saa bi to Aa lAibrerite pAoYA yAYanAa, kenAo sambhaa naYaa। ki karA yAYaa? elabAkiYAa Thia karalo kampiuTArea khu.NTinATi shikhe nijea yA yA darakAa binAmUlye DAunaloa kare nebea। agatyA nijea cheshTAa hyAki.n shekhAa। kintu eirakaa lobhaniia pratibhA ki Aa chApA thAkea? kalea ju.Dae bandhudea AbadAa Asate lAgaloa, chalalo gopanea tAdero praYojaniia biYea chAhidA meTAnoa।
eraa bhAbei bhAlo chalaCia sabakiCua। erapaa meYeTi pa.Daate gea rAshiYAa, AmerikAa, tArapaa AbAa nijea deshe phire eloa। gabeshaNA karate giYe dekhalo ea adbhua jinisaa। kono ekajaa gabeshaa anea khATuni kare kiCu ekaTA phaa pelaa, seTA se ea gabeshaNA patrikA bA jArnAle prakAshanAa jana pAThAloa। saa ThikaThAa thAkale gabeshaNApatraTi prakAa habea। e paryana Thia ACe sabakiCua, kono TAkAa lenadea neia। ebAa yadi anyakeu sei gabeshaNApatraTi pa.Daate chAYaa, tAke sei nirdisha prakAshakea kACe beshakiCu TAkA diYe sei pepAraTi pa.Daate habea। ekhaa ki haYaa, AmAdea desha-abideshea bishbabidyAlaa bA gabeshaNAgAragulo sarakArea theke pAoYA anudAa theke bea kiCu gabeshaNApatrikA pa.DaAa jana baCaa baCaa prakAshanA s.nsthAguloke moTA TAkA diYe sAbaskrAia kare rAkhea। kintu yadi kono pratyana anchalea keu nijea kAjea jana seisaa pepAa pa.Daate chAYaa? athabA kono CAta bA CAtrii bA.Daite base pa.DaAshonA karate chAa kono jArnAa thekea? milabenA milabenAa। elabAkiYAa gea kshepea। 2a0a1aa sAle tairi karalo sAi-ahAa bA balA yAa binAmUlye risAra pepAa pa.DaAa sbargarAjyaa। tAa dAbi jnAa kakhano TAkA diYe kiCu mushTimea prakAshakea kACe siimAbada kea thAkabea?
prakAshakarA uThalo regea, tAdea byAbasA puro mATi hoYAa jogA.Daaa। shuru halo elabAkiYAnea biruddhe mAmalAa। sabAa Age tA.DaA karalo bijnAnea sabacheYe baa prakAshanA s.nsthA elasabhiYAa Aa AmerikAa kemikyAa sosAiTia, 1aa miliYaa DalArea mAmalA karalo oa biruddhea। mAmalA chalaloa, AdAlaa prakAshanA s.nsthAa pakshei rAa diloa, kAraa seTAi AinasaNgataa। eTA AbAa haa nAkia, koTi koTi TAkA 'adAmaa' yei gabeshaNApatrea tA binAmUlye CAta CAtriidea bitaraa karabea, emaa alukshune kathA keu shuneCea? agatyA ajnAtabAa elabAkiYAneraa। takhaa theke ei chalaCea, emanaki yakhaa nechAa prakAshanii tAke 2a0a1aa sAle bijnAa o prayuktia jagate Alo.Daaa sRRishTikArii prathaa 1a0ajaa byAktia tAlikAa phelaloa, takhano pRRithibiia sAmane hAjia hate pAreni sea, sambaa shudhu ekaTi skAia inTArabhiua।
shudhu AlekajAndrAi naYaa, ei tAlikAa Aro nAa ACea, eraa soYArjaa, eDoYAra snoDenaa, ACe lAibreri jenesia ea mataa oYebasAiTaa। ichCe hale edea samparke pa.Dae dekhabenaa, AshA kari bhAlo lAgabea।
sbargea theke mAnushea jana Agua niYe AsAa jana pramithiua ye kashTakaa mRRityuyantraNA bhoa kareCilaa, bA jnAnabRRikshea Apea khAoYAa jana Adamea shAstia, eisaa AmAdea shekhAYaa, jnAa kakhano sarbasAdhAraNea jana nijea kshati kare Aharaa karate neia। yArA esaa kare samAa tAdea bokA balea। shurutei baleCilAmaa, meYeTi bokA Cilaa।
punashchaa: bideshi nAmagulo nijea mato kare uchchAraa kare bA.nlAa likheCia, bhua hale shudhare debenaa। sAi-ahAa oYebasAia Tia Domeia anekabAa badaa haYeCea, nishedhAjnAa kAraNe mUa oYebasAia Tio rAshiYAa bhAshAa bAnAnoa। ekhano pratidia kaYea lAa gabeshaa ei oYebasAiTea sAhAyye gabeshaNAa kAa karenaa।
